short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension to clear browser data

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Take control of your online privacy with the Clear Browser Data extension! Designed for users who want to keep their browsing experience clean and secure, this handy tool allows you to easily delete unwanted data from your browser history. Whether you're looking to clear your cache, cookies, or browsing history, this extension simplifies the process with just a few clicks.
